[Gemini]: The regular expression at `src/werkzeug/http.py`, lines 30-48, is vulnerable to Regular Expression Denial of Service (ReDoS). The vulnerability lies in the pattern `(?:[ \\t]*;[ \\t]* (?:[^\\s;,q][^\\s;,]* | q[^\\s;,=][^\\s;,]*) )*`, which is used for parsing `Accept` headers. This pattern exhibits catastrophic backtracking due to nested quantifiers where the inner repetition `[^\\s;,]*` is inside an outer repetition `(...)*`.

